== 敘述 ==
Template for a direct linking to records in the GESTIS Substance Database of the {{tsl|en|Institute for Occupational Safety and Health||IFA}}

Usage in articles on chemicals, especially for citing chemical properties using [[帮助:脚注|references]]

=== 參數 ===
* <code>ZVG</code>: the ZVG number is a record number internally used in the GESTIS Substance Database
* <code>CAS</code>: the [[CAS号|CAS registry number]]
* <code>Name</code>: name of the substance (optional)
* <code>Date</code>: the date of the (last) access to the database

<code>ZVG</code> and <code>CAS</code> can be used concurrently, but one of them is sufficient. <code>Date</code> is intended to be filled in.

== 使用 ==
<code><nowiki>{{GESTIS|ZVG= |CAS= |Name= |Date= }}</nowiki></code>

or inside a reference

<code><nowiki><ref name="GESTIS">{{GESTIS|ZVG= |CAS= |Name= |Date= }}</ref></nowiki></code>

=== 一般範例 ===
<code><nowiki>{{GESTIS|ZVG=14280|CAS=102-71-6|Date=21 October 2007}}</nowiki></code>

results in

{{GESTIS|ZVG=14280|CAS=102-71-6|Date=21 October 2007}}

